    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2 id="summary-measure-reporting">Summary Measure Reporting</h2>

<p>When the results of a quality measure are completed for a population at the end of a reporting period, they are POSTed to the quality measure Receiverâ€™s FHIR Server. The report may only consist of the Summary MeasureReport in which case it is POSTed to the MeasureReport endpoint.  If there are other referenced resources all the resources are bundled together as a set of <code class="highlighter-rouge">POST</code> interactions and sent as a single <a href="http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/http.html#transaction">transaction</a> interaction using the Standard FHIR API.</p>

